const getCurrentForecastDetails = (main, wind) => ({
    temp: (main.temp - 273.15) * 9/5 + 32,
    pressure: main.pressure * 0.029529983071445,
    humidity: main.humidity,
    min_temp: (main.temp_min - 273.15) * 9/5 + 32,
    max_temp: (main.temp_max - 273.15) * 9/5 + 32,
    wind: wind.speed * 2.237
})

export default getCurrentForecastDetails
